Message.MsgText: RESOLVER_UNABLE_TO_REMOVE_CONFIG_REPOSITORY_EXCEPTION=CWSAO0006E: An internal error occurred. Cannot remove the configured repository with URL {0} from the RepositoryAdmin service. Exception: {1}
RESOLVER_SERVICE_UNAVAILABLE=CWSAO0001E: An internal error occurred. Cannot provision the enterprise bundle archive (EBA) {0} because service {1} is unavailable.
RESOLVER_UNABLE_TO_LOCATE_RESOURCE=CWSAO0014E: The resource with symbolic name {0} and version {1} could not be identified in the repository.
Message.Explanation: The runtime environment attempted to identify some application or use-bundle content, but could not find it in any bundle repository. The most common cause is that the content has been removed from the repository. This might mean that the application is unable to resolve in the future.
Message.UserResponse: Add the missing bundle to a configured bundle repository.

Message.MsgText: RESOLVER_UNABLE_TO_ADD_CONFIG_REPOSITORY_WARNING=CWSAO0013W: Cannot add the configured bundle repository with URL {0} to the resolver. Exception: {1}
Message.Explanation: An bundle repository could not be added to the resolver. The most common cause is that the repository URL is not valid.
Message.UserResponse: Check that the bundle repository URL is valid and that the bundle repository is well-formed.

Message.MsgText: RESOLVER_IOEXCEPTION=CWSAO0002E: An internal error occurred. The EBA archive {0} cannot be provisioned because the local repository file {1} cannot be created.
RESOLVER_UNABLE_TO_ADD_CONFIG_REPOSITORY_EXCEPTION=CWSAO0004E: An internal error occurred. Cannot add the configured repository with URL {0} to the RepositoryAdmin service. Exception: {1}
RESOLVER_UNABLE_TO_ADD_REPOSITORY_EXCEPTION=CWSAO0003E: An internal error occurred. When provisioning the EBA archive {0}, cannot add the repository {1} to the RepositoryAdmin service.
RESOLVER_UNABLE_TO_RESOLVE=CWSAO0007E: The system cannot provision the EBA {0} because the following problems in the dependency chain were detected: {1}
Message.Explanation: The full set of dependencies for an enterprise bundle archive (EBA) cannot be resolved.
Message.UserResponse: See the accompanying messages for information about the dependencies that cannot be provisioned. Correct the problems, reinstall the EBA, and try again.

Message.MsgText: RESOLVER_UNABLE_TO_REMOVE_REPOSITORY_EXCEPTION=CWSAO0005E: An internal error occurred. When provisioning the EBA archive {0}, cannot remove repository {1} from the RepositoryAdmin service.
RESOLVER_UNABLE_HANDLE_FRAGMENT_HOST_WITH_EXTENSION=CWSAO0008E: Cannot attach the fragment host {0} because it has an extension directive.
Message.Explanation: Cannot attach a fragment that has an extension directive set. Applications must not set this directive. The extension directive applies only when the Fragment-Host is the System Bundle.
Message.UserResponse: Remove the extension directive from the application.
